OL,3,CTata and British Steel bosses to sit
OL,4,Con new steel council
OL,6,FThe UK Government has launched a new
OL,7,Fsteel council with members including
OL,8,FTata Steel and British Steel following
OL,9,Fthousands of job losses in the UK last
OL,10,Fyear.
OL,12,FThe Steel Council will help steer
OL,13,Fplans for the industry which will be
OL,14,Fbacked by up to #2.5 billion of
OL,15,Finvestment.
OL,17,FBusiness Secretary Jonathan Reynolds,
OL,18,Fwho will chair the council's first
OL,19,Fmeeting on Tuesday, said steel
OL,20,Fcommunities have "had enough of
OL,21,Flurching from crisis to crisis".
