OL,3,CTata and British Steel bosses to sit
OL,4,Con new steel council
OL,6,FTraditional steelmaking ceased in
OL,7,FSeptember, with thousands of workers
OL,8,Flosing their jobs. British Steel also
OL,9,Fannounced it would close blast
OL,10,Ffurnaces in Scunthorpe in 2023, and
OL,11,Funveiled plans to roll out a less
OL,12,Fpolluting electric arc furnace.
OL,14,FThe plans, which are greener but
OL,15,Frequire fewer workers to keep them
OL,16,Fgoing, raised fears over potentially
OL,17,Fthousands of job losses. The Labour
OL,18,FGovernment has vowed to spend #2.5
OL,19,Fbillion "to rebuild the steel
OL,20,Findustry".
