OL,3,CTata and British Steel bosses to sit
OL,4,Con new steel council
OL,6,FThe money would sit alongside a
OL,7,Fseparate #500 million package for Tata
OL,8,FSteel to part-fund the new steel
OL,9,Fproduction at Port Talbot.
OL,11,FThe Steel Council, co-chaired by the
OL,12,Fchairman of Teesside-based Materials
OL,13,FProcessing Institute, is set to work
OL,14,Ftoward the launch of the Government's
OL,15,Fsteel strategy in spring.
OL,17,FThis strategy is expected to set out
OL,18,Fhow steel capacity can be increased in
OL,19,Fthe UK and how investment decisions
OL,20,Fcan meet demand and boost economic
OL,21,Fgrowth.
