OL,6,F"With the launch of the Steel Council
OL,7,Fwe're placing workers and local
OL,8,Fcommunities at the heart of our plans
OL,9,Fas we bring forward _2.5 billion of
OL,10,Finvestment to secure growth right
OL,11,Facross the country."
