OL,3,CTata and British Steel bosses to sit
OL,4,Con new steel council
OL,6,FGareth Stace, director general of
OL,7,Ftrade group UK Steel, said: "The
OL,8,Festablishment of the Steel Council
OL,9,Fmarks a defining moment for the future
OL,10,Fof steelmaking in Britain. The council
OL,11,Frepresents a crucial step towards
OL,12,Fcreating a comprehensive Government
OL,13,Fsteel strategy - one that lays the
OL,14,Ffoundations for a sustainable and
OL,15,Fresilient industry."
